-- Redeem Tests

Test "Mint then Redeem All"
    NewComptroller
    ListedEtherToken slETH initialExchangeRate:0.005e9
    CallMintEth Geoff 0.005e18 slETH
    -- Check current affairs
    Assert Equal (Erc20 slETH TokenBalance Geoff) 10e8
    Assert Equal (SLToken slETH UnderlyingBalance Geoff) 0.005e18
    Invariant Static (SLToken slETH ExchangeRateStored)
    -- Now redeem after some time
    FastForward 2 Blocks
    Expect Changes (EtherBalance Geoff) +0.005e18
    RedeemUnderlyingEth Geoff 0.005e18 slETH
    Assert Equal (Erc20 slETH TokenBalance Geoff) Zero
    Assert Equal (SLToken slETH UnderlyingBalance Geoff) Zero

