    Prep Geoff 50e18 ZRX slETH
    Mint Geoff 50e18 slETH
    Assert Equal (Erc20 slETH TokenBalance Geoff) 500e8
    Assert Equal (SLToken slETH UnderlyingBalance Geoff) 50e18
    Assert Equal (SLToken slETH ExchangeRate) 1e9
    -- Get some brah to borrow then repay
