    -- We've accrued 10% interest for 5 blocks, or 50% of the amount,
    --   thus, we should have accrued 5e18 of interest for the protocol
    --   This is due pro-rata to all holders, but we just have one, so
    --   let's check that account is given correct new balance.
    Assert Equal (Erc20 slETH TokenBalance Geoff) 500e8
    Assert Equal (SLToken slETH UnderlyingBalance Geoff) 55e18
    Assert Equal (SLToken slETH ExchangeRate) 1.1e9
    -- Now redeem all with interest
